---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - DevUtil" description="Privacy policy for DevUtil developer utilities">
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
    <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> / DevUtil
  </p>

  <h1>DevUtil Privacy Policy</h1>
  <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top: 0;">Privacy-First Developer Utilities</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">Last Updated: December 2025</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    DevUtil is a comprehensive, privacy-first collection of developer utilities for everyday tasks—all running 
    locally in your browser.
  </p>

  <h2>Privacy-First Design</h2>
  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <strong>100% Client-Side Processing</strong><br />
    All tools run entirely in your browser. Your data never leaves your device.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Collection</h2>
  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <strong>DevUtil collects ZERO data.</strong>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>No server calls</li>
    <li>No data transmission</li>
    <li>No analytics or tracking</li>
    <li>No cookies</li>
    <li>No user accounts</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How Tools Work</h2>
  <p>
    Every utility in DevUtil processes data entirely in your browser using JavaScript:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Encoders/Decoders run client-side only</li>
    <li>Code formatters process locally</li>
    <li>Converters operate in-browser</li>
    <li>Generators create data locally</li>
    <li>All results stay on your device</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Offline Capability</h2>
  <p>
    DevUtil works completely offline after the initial page load. This proves that no data is being sent to servers.
  </p>

  <h2>Open Source</h2>
  <p>
    DevUtil is open source. You can inspect the code to verify our privacy claims:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Full transparency</li>
    <li>No hidden tracking scripts</li>
    <li>Auditable source code</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>None.</strong> DevUtil does not integrate with any third-party services, analytics platforms, or external APIs.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Storage</h2>
  <p>
    Some tools may use browser localStorage or sessionStorage to save user preferences (like theme settings). 
    This data never leaves your browser and can be cleared anytime.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy inquiries, contact us at:<br />
    <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dps.manit@gmail.com">dps.manit@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p><a href="/privacy">← Back to Master Privacy Policy</a></p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
